images.description:
Do you ever get that? You go to do something mundane like food shopping and you stumble upon a gem of an object and all over the sudden, you are visualising a photo layout light background etc? 
So I was doing my weekly food shopping on one Friday evening and came across those pink barley sweets. 
I couldn’t resist! For about  £0.75 I had 2h of pure joy and creativity. I hope you like the photo :)
